<article class="post--single post-690 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-cookies-course category-desserts category-fall category-perennial-favorite category-snacks category-spring category-summer category-vegetarian category-winter tag-baking tag-everyday-cooking tag-good-to-the-grain tag-kim-boyce ingredients-brown-sugar ingredients-butter ingredients-chocolate ingredients-whole-wheat" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
