    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi Molly, I have never posted on your blog before.  I want to write first of all that I love substituting wheat flour in all my recipes (in fact it&#39;s the only kind of flour in my freezer) and am looking forward to trying these cookies.  Also, I loved your book and wanted you to know it has inspired me very much in my cooking.  I now make my own salad dressing and I grew my own roma tomatoes this year just to make your recipe for slow roasted tomatoes.  They turned out wonderful!  I have always tried to stew my tomatoes in water and these were so much better &#8211; like all the flavor of the whole tomatoe was concentrated into one bite.  So, I wanted to thank you for the inspiration &#8211; you have a way of describing food that makes me want to cook and eat!</p>
