      <p>I might have to pretend that I didn&#39;t down an entire package of McVitie&#39;s last week and make these.  I am a child of the 70&#39;s and early 80&#39;s, which means  my mother often made chocolate chip cookies with whole wheat flour (and raw sugar) when I was growing up, so i&#39;m sure these will smack of nostalgia.  I&#39;m pretty sold on my own brown butter brown sugar cookies though.  maybe a tasteoff.</p>
