    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>hi molly,</p>
<p>I have read almost all your entries from the start, have bought and loved your book, and have been finally tempted to make these cookies.  I live in the uk and absolutely looove digestives, so there was no choice but to make them!  I halved the recipe except that I forgot to use 1 egg instead of two, so the cookies spread into giant cookies.  Plus because of my ridiculous oven, burnt half of the batch&#8230;but my god, I eat about 4 of them per day (even the burnt ones!!).  They&#39;re absolutely addictive!</p>
